[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    169[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Fix:** Adopt the archive-reference discipline uniformly across the longitudinal store, the support-decision-record journal, the sensitive-disclosure store, the crisis-event record, the conversation log, and the tool-call ledger on the real-time hot path:
